2. ADD USER & GROUP

3. MKDIR dirs -> CHOWN

4. build startup -> COPY -> CHOWN ROOT:ROOT -> CHMOD a=xs

5. COPY Templates -> CHOWN ROOT:ROOT -> CHMOD a=r

6. COPY ENTRYPOINT

